import * as React from "react"
import { View } from "react-native"
import { color, spacing } from "../../theme"
import { Transaction } from "../../types/transaction"
import { Divider } from "../divider/divider"
import { Text } from "../../components"

export interface TransactionListItemProps {
    transaction: Transaction,
}

export function TransactionListItem(props: TransactionListItemProps) {
    const { transaction } = props
    return (
        <View>
            <Divider />
            <View style={{ display: 'flex' }}>
                <View style={{ width: 60, height: 60, backgroundColor: 'green' }} />
                <Text text={transaction.title} preset="medium" ellipsizeMode="tail" />
                <Text text={transaction.date} preset="small" />
                <Text text={`${transaction.contributors.length} People`} preset="small" />
                <Text text={`Created by ${transaction.owner.firstName} ${transaction.owner.lastName}`} preset="small" />
                <Text text={`$${transaction.totalPrice}`} preset="medium" />
            </View>
            <Divider />
        </View>

    )
}
